{"id":186,"parent_id":174,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":186,"title":"Helaman 12","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hel.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 12"],[".studySummary",["i","Men are unstable and foolish and quick to do evil—The Lord chastens His people—The nothingness of men is compared with the power of God—In the day of judgment, men will gain everlasting life or everlasting damnation. About 6",["span.small","B.C."]]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1","order":"05.21.012.19984"},["b","1"],"And thus we can behold how false, and also the unsteadiness of the hearts of the children of men; yea, we can see that the Lord in his great infinite goodness doth bless and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"prosper"],"those who put their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"trust"],"in him."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2","order":"05.21.012.19985"},["b","2"],"Yea, and we may see at the very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"time"],"when he doth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"prosper"],"his people, yea, in the increase of their fields, their flocks and their herds, and in gold, and in silver, and in all manner of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"precious"],"things of every kind and art; sparing their lives, and delivering them out of the hands of their enemies; softening the hearts of their enemies that they should not declare wars against them; yea, and in fine, doing all things for the welfare and happiness of his people; yea, then is the time that they do",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"harden"],"their hearts, and do",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"forget"],"the Lord their God, and do",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_2f"},"trample"],"under their feet the Holy One—yea, and this because of their ease, and their exceedingly great prosperity."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3","order":"05.21.012.19986"},["b","3"],"And thus we see that except the Lord doth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"chasten"],"his people with many afflictions, yea, except he doth visit them with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"death"],"and with terror, and with famine and with all manner of pestilence, they will not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"remember"],"him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4","order":"05.21.012.19987"},["b","4"],"O how",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"foolish"],", and how vain, and how evil, and devilish, and how",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"quick"],"to do iniquity, and how slow to do good, are the children of men; yea, how quick to hearken unto the words of the evil one, and to set their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"hearts"],"upon the vain things of the world!"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.5","order":"05.21.012.19988"},["b","5"],"Yea, how quick to be lifted up in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"pride"],"; yea, how quick to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"boast"],", and do all manner of that which is iniquity; and how slow are they to remember the Lord their God, and to give ear unto his counsels, yea, how slow to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"walk"],"in wisdom’s paths!"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.6","order":"05.21.012.19989"},["b","6"],"Behold, they do not desire that the Lord their God, who hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"created"],"them, should",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"rule"],"and reign over them; notwithstanding his great goodness and his mercy towards them, they do set at",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"naught"],"his counsels, and they will not that he should be their guide."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.7","order":"05.21.012.19990"},["b","7"],"O how great is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"nothingness"],"of the children of men; yea, even they are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"less"],"than the dust of the earth."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.8","order":"05.21.012.19991"},["b","8"],"For behold, the dust of the earth moveth hither and thither, to the dividing asunder, at the command of our great and everlasting God."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.9","order":"05.21.012.19992"},["b","9"],"Yea, behold at his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"voice"],"do the hills and the mountains tremble and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"quake"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.10","order":"05.21.012.19993"},["b","10"],"And by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"power"],"of his voice they are broken up, and become smooth, yea, even like unto a valley."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.11","order":"05.21.012.19994"},["b","11"],"Yea, by the power of his voice doth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"whole"],"earth shake;"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.12","order":"05.21.012.19995"},["b","12"],"Yea, by the power of his voice, do the foundations rock, even to the very center."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.13","order":"05.21.012.19996"},["b","13"],"Yea, and if he say unto the earth—Move—it is moved."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.14","order":"05.21.012.19997"},["b","14"],"Yea, if he say unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"earth"],"—Thou shalt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"go back"],", that it",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"lengthen"],"out the day for many hours—it is done;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.15","order":"05.21.012.19998"},["b","15"],"And thus, according to his word the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"earth"],"goeth back, and it appeareth unto man that the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"sun"],"standeth still; yea, and behold, this is so; for surely it is the earth that moveth and not the sun."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.16","order":"05.21.012.19999"},["b","16"],"And behold, also, if he say unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"waters"],"of the great deep—",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Be"],"thou dried up—it is done."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.17","order":"05.21.012.20000"},["b","17"],"Behold, if he say unto this mountain—Be thou raised up, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"come"],"over and fall upon that city, that it be buried up—behold it is done."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.18","order":"05.21.012.20001"},["b","18"],"And behold, if a man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"hide"],"up a treasure in the earth, and the Lord shall say—Let it be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"accursed"],", because of the iniquity of him who hath hid it up—behold, it shall be accursed."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.19","order":"05.21.012.20002"},["b","19"],"And if the Lord shall say—Be thou accursed, that no man shall find thee from this time henceforth and forever—behold, no man getteth it henceforth and forever."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.20","order":"05.21.012.20003"},["b","20"],"And behold, if the Lord shall say unto a man—Because of thine iniquities, thou shalt be accursed",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"forever"],"—it shall be done."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.21","order":"05.21.012.20004"},["b","21"],"And if the Lord shall say—Because of thine iniquities thou shalt be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"cut off"],"from my presence—he will cause that it shall be so."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.22","order":"05.21.012.20005"},["b","22"],"And wo unto him to whom he shall say this, for it shall be unto him that will do iniquity, and he cannot be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"saved"],"; therefore, for this cause, that men might be saved, hath repentance been declared."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.23","order":"05.21.012.20006"},["b","23"],"Therefore, blessed are they who will repent and hearken unto the voice of the Lord their God; for these are they that shall be saved."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.24","order":"05.21.012.20007"},["b","24"],"And may God grant, in his great fulness, that men might be brought unto repentance and good works, that they might be restored unto grace for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"grace"],", according to their works."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.25","order":"05.21.012.20008"},["b","25"],"And I would that all men might be saved. But we read that in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"great"],"and last day there are some who shall be cast out, yea, who shall be cast off from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"presence"],"of the Lord;"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.26","order":"05.21.012.20009"},["b","26"],"Yea, who shall be consigned to a state of endless misery, fulfilling the words which say: They that have done good shall have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"everlasting life"],"; and they that have done evil shall have everlasting",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"damnation"],". And thus it is. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1a","order":"05.21.012.20010"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/26.5"},"2 Chr. 26:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/1.3.2-3"},"Ps. 1:3 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1b","order":"05.21.012.20012"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/36.7.7-8"},"Ps. 36:7 (7–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/22.2"},"2 Ne. 22:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.6"},"Mosiah 4:6"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/trust-in-god"},"TG Trust in God"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2a","order":"05.21.012.20014"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.8"},"Alma 46:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.26"},"Hel. 4:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/6.32"},"6:32"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2b","order":"05.21.012.20016"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/62.10"},"Ps. 62:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2c","order":"05.21.012.20018"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2d","order":"05.21.012.20020"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2e","order":"05.21.012.20022"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/8.11.10-20"},"Deut. 8:11 (10–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2f","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.2f","order":"05.21.012.20024"},["b","2f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.53"},"Alma 5:53"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.35"},"3 Ne. 28:35"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3a","order":"05.21.012.20026"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.2.1-8"},"Deut. 11:2 (1–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.26"},"Ezek. 20:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/23.21"},"Mosiah 23:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.21"},"D&C 98:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.8"},"101:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3b","order":"05.21.012.20028"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.34"},"Ps. 78:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3c","order":"05.21.012.20030"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.6.6-11"},"Amos 4:6 (6–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/2.7"},"Jonah 2:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.17"},"Mosiah 1:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4a","order":"05.21.012.20032"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/foolishness"},"TG Foolishness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4b","order":"05.21.012.20034"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/32.8"},"Ex. 32:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/2.17"},"Judg. 2:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.7"},"Isa. 59:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.22"},"Jer. 4:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.4c","order":"05.21.012.20036"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/6.5"},"Gen. 6:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/15.19"},"Matt. 15:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/3.12"},"Heb. 3:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.5a","order":"05.21.012.20038"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/29.23"},"Prov. 29:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.5b","order":"05.21.012.20040"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.5c","order":"05.21.012.20042"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.6a","order":"05.21.012.20044"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.9.9-10"},"Isa. 45:9 (9–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.30"},"D&C 58:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.6b","order":"05.21.012.20046"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/8.23.22-23"},"Judg. 8:23 (22–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/60.4"},"D&C 60:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.6c","order":"05.21.012.20048"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/8.7"},"Jer. 8:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.7a","order":"05.21.012.20050"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/40.17.15,17"},"Isa. 40:17 (15, 17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/4.35"},"Dan. 4:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.10"},"Moses 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.7b","order":"05.21.012.20052"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.27"},"Gen. 18:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.9a","order":"05.21.012.20054"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.24"},"Ezek. 1:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.9b","order":"05.21.012.20056"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/5.5"},"Judg. 5:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/22.10"},"3 Ne. 22:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.10a","order":"05.21.012.20058"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.46"},"1 Ne. 17:46"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.11a","order":"05.21.012.20060"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/5.23"},"Morm. 5:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.9"},"Ether 4:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.14a","order":"05.21.012.20062"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/10.12.12-14"},"Josh. 10:12 (12–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.14b","order":"05.21.012.20064"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/38.8.7-8"},"Isa. 38:8 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.14c","order":"05.21.012.20066"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/20.9.8-11"},"2 Kgs. 20:9 (8–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.15a","order":"05.21.012.20068"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/30.44"},"Alma 30:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.15b","order":"05.21.012.20070"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.11"},"Hab. 3:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.16a","order":"05.21.012.20072"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.27.23-27"},"Matt. 8:27 (23–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.9"},"Jacob 4:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.16b","order":"05.21.012.20074"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.27"},"Isa. 44:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.10"},"51:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.17a","order":"05.21.012.20076"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/8.10.10,25"},"3 Ne. 8:10 (10, 25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/9.8.5-6,8"},"9:8 (5–6, 8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.18a","order":"05.21.012.20078"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.18.18-23"},"Hel. 13:18 (18–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.18.17-19"},"Morm. 1:18 (17–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/14.1"},"Ether 14:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.18b","order":"05.21.012.20080"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.17"},"Hel. 13:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.20a","order":"05.21.012.20082"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/27.31"},"Mosiah 27:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.21a","order":"05.21.012.20084"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/23.39.39-40"},"Jer. 23:39 (39–40)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.4"},"D&C 63:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.22a","order":"05.21.012.20086"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"TG Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.24a","order":"05.21.012.20088"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/grace"},"TG Grace"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.25a","order":"05.21.012.20090"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.5"},"Mal. 4:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.4"},"3 Ne. 26:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.25b","order":"05.21.012.20092"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.26a","order":"05.21.012.20094"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/12.2.2-3"},"Dan. 12:2 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.7"},"D&C 19:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.26b","order":"05.21.012.20096"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/damnation"},"TG Damnation"],"."]]}
